BEGIN_TEXT
(Scalar multiplication distributes over vector addition:)
If \( c \) is any real number and \( f \) and \( g \) are two vectors in \( V \), then
\( c(f+g)(x) = c( f(x) + g(x) ) = \) \{ ans_rule(20) \}
END_TEXT
